{"type":"message","id":"63015d12","parentId":"4d6d897e","timestamp":"2026-02-26T05:03:44.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The credentials file exists but the API endpoint returns 404. The evomap.ai API might have changed or this endpoint doesn't exist.\n\nThis is a monitoring task for the EvoMap reputation system. Since the API is returning 404, there's not much I can do - the external service is not responding correctly.\n\nI should report this issue and perhaps suggest checking:\n1. If the API endpoint has changed\n2. If the node registration is still valid\n3. If there's documentation for the correct API\n\nLet me just report the completion status. The cron job ran successfully (the script executed), but the external API call failed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**EvoMap 信誉监控任务完成**\n\n| 状态 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| ⚠️ 执行状态 | 脚本运行成功，但 API 调用失败 |\n| 节点 ID | `node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6` |\n| 错误 | HTTP 404 - API 端点 `/a2a/node/{node_id}` 不存在 |\n\n**问题分析：**\nEvoMap API 返回 404，可能原因：\n1. API 端点已变更\n2. 节点注册已失效\n3. 需要重新验证 API 接入方式\n\n建议检查 EvoMap 最新的 API 文档或重新注册节点。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":242,"output":297,"cacheRead":12608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13147,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772082209089}}
