{"type":"message","id":"9766b48f","parentId":"7470d2ca","timestamp":"2026-02-26T17:01:31.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job is running again. The previous execution failed with a 404 error because the API endpoint doesn't exist. I should run the script again to see if there's any change, but likely it will fail again with the same error.\n\nLet me just execute it and report the result.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a7039fda0b074039b7b3b8a6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-reputation-monitor.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2693,"output":87,"cacheRead":10176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12956,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772125283031}}
{"type":"message","id":"9eb1c755","parentId":"9766b48f","timestamp":"2026-02-26T17:01:31.484Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a7039fda0b074039b7b3b8a6","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"═══════════════════════════════════════════\n  EvoMap 信誉监控任务\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n节点: node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6\n别名: N/A\n\n正在获取节点状态...\n\n❌ 获取节点状态失败: HTTP 404: {\"error\":\"route_not_found\",\"message\":\"No route matches GET /a2a/node/node_evomap_op_5b4efaf43f2c16c6.\",\"suggestions\":[{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/assets/semantic-search\",\"description\":\"Vector similarity search (?q=...)\",\"similarity\":0.33999999999999997},{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/assets/graph-search\",\"description\":\"Knowledge graph search\",\"similarity\":0.32},{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/deliberation/:id/status\",\"description\":\"Deliberation status\",\"similarity\":0.32},{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/work/available\",\"description\":\"Available work (?node_id)\",\"similarity\":0.32}],\"help\":{\"documentation\":\"GET /a2a/skill\",\"api_reference\":\"GET /llms-full.txt\",\"route_catalog\":\"GET /.well-known/api-catalog\"},\"available_in_category\":{\"name\":\"A2A Protocol & Agent API\",\"prefix\":\"/a2a\",\"description\":\"Core agent-to-agent protocol and REST discovery. Protocol endpoints (hello, publish, fetch, report, decision, revoke) require the GEP-A2A envelope; all others are plain REST JSON.\",\"routes\":[{\"method\":\"GET\",\"path\":\"/a2a/skill\",\"description\":\"Protocol docs -- ?topic=<id> for detail\"},{\"method\":\"POST\",\"path\":\"/a2a/skill/search\",\"description\":\"Semantic doc+web search (costs credits)\"},{\"method\":\"POST\",\"path\":\"/a2a/hello\",\"description\":\"Register agent node (envelope)\"},{\"method\":\"POST\",\"path\":\"/a2a/heartbeat\",\"description\":\"Keep-alive heartbeat\"},{\"method\":\"POST\",\"path\":\"/a2a/publish\",\"description\":\"Publish Gene+Capsule bundle (env