{"type":"message","id":"b3ae94cc","parentId":"f756d511","timestamp":"2026-02-26T17:02:20.716Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"节点状态获取成功了！显示：\n- 状态: active\n- 信誉: N/A\n- GDI 分数: N/A\n- 资产数量: 0\n- 调用次数: 0\n\n但是排行榜端点 `/a2a/leaderboard` 不存在。我需要更新脚本，使用 `/a2a/nodes` 来获取排名信息，或者直接移除排行榜功能。\n\n让我更新脚本，把排行榜改为使用 `/a2a/nodes` 端点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"节点状态获取成功！排行榜端点需要更新为 `/a2a/nodes`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7d586cdba40847aa86ecc7b7","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-reputation-monitor.js","oldText":"// 获取排行榜\nfunction fetchLeaderboard(credentials) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const options = {\n      hostname: 'evomap.ai',\n      port: 443,\n      path: '/a2a/leaderboard?limit=100',\n      method: 'GET',\n      headers: {\n        'X-Node-ID': credentials.node_id\n      }\n    };\n    \n    const req = https.request(options, (res) => {\n      let body = '';\n      res.on('data', (chunk) => { body += chunk; });\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        if (res.statusCode === 200) {\n          try {\n            const result = JSON.parse(body);\n            resolve(result.leaderboard || []);\n          } catch (e) {\n            reject(new Error('Invalid response: ' + body));\n          }\n        } else {\n          reject(new Error(`HTTP ${res.statusCode}: ${body}`));\n        }\n      });\n    });\n    \n    req.on('error', reject);\n    req.setTimeout(30000, () => {\n      req.destroy();\n      reject(new Error('Request timeout'));\n    });\n    \n    req.end();\n  });\n}","newText":"// 获取节点列表（用于排名）\nfunction fetchNodesList(credentials) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const options = {\n      hostname: 'evomap.ai',\n      port: 443,\n      path: '/a2a/nodes?limit=100',\n      method: 'GET',\n      headers: {\n        'X-Node-ID': credentials.node_id\n      }\n    };\n\n    const req = https.request(options, (res) => {\n      let body = '';\n      res.on('data', (chunk) => { body += chunk; });\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        if (res.statusCode === 200) {\n          try {\n            const result = JSON.parse(body);\n            resolve(result.nodes || result || []);\n          } catch (e) {\n            reject(new Error('Invalid response: ' + body));\n          }\n        } else {\n          reject(new Error(`HTTP ${res.statusCode}: ${body}`));\n        }\n      });\n    });\n\n    req.on('error', reject);\n    req.setTimeout(30000, () => {\n      req.destroy();\n      reject(new Error('Request timeout'));\n    });\n\n    req.end();\n  });\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2757,"output":650,"cacheRead":15680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19087,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772125318176}}
